DESCRIPTION: Edit any element (for example the description) of an existing embed that was originally sent by Gamer bot.
EXTENDED_LINE_1: To get the ID of a message, make sure that Developer Mode is on in your client and right click the message whose code you'd like to copy and select **Copy ID**.
EXTENDED_LINE_2: **{{prefix}}embedset [Message ID] [Embed Element] [New Value] ** ~ Updates the Element you provided to the new value you provided.
ALIASES: Embedset does not have any aliases.
NO_EMBED: The message you provided is not an embed I can edit.
NEED_ARGS: Invalid Input, please consult the help page and try again.
